#: ../../migration.rst:9
msgid ""
"Migration is the process to convert a NethServer 7 machine (*source*) "
"into a NethServer 8 (*destination*)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:11
msgid "Before starting you will need:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:13
msgid "SSH and Cockpit access to the source NethServer 7 machine"
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:14
msgid ""
"a new server containing a :ref:`freshly installed NethServer 8 cluster "
"<install-section>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:16
msgid "Also make sure that"
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:18
msgid ""
"if the source is connected to an external account provider, such account "
"provider is reachable also from the destination"
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:20
msgid ""
"you have access to your authoritative DNS server: you will need to change"
" some DNS records after the migration of each application"
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:24
msgid ""
"The migration procedure will add the source machine as special node of "
"NethServer 8 cluster."
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:26
msgid ""
"First, you are going to install the migration tool on the source machine."
" Access the source server using SSH as root user, then execute: ::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:31
msgid ""
"You can now open the just installed ``NS8 migration`` application from "
"Cockpit."
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:33
msgid ""
"Now, connect the NethServer 7 server to an existing new NethServer 8 "
"cluster by entering the following fields:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:35
msgid ""
"``NS8 leader node``: the host name or IP address of NethServer 8 cluster "
"leader node"
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:36
msgid ""
"``NS8 admin username`` and ``NS8 admin password``: administrator "
"credentials for the leader node"
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:37
msgid ""
"uncheck the ``TLS validation`` option if the leader node does not have a "
"valid TLS certificate"
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:39
msgid "Then, click the :guilabel:`Connect` button."
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:41
msgid ""
"The web interface will display the list of all applications installed "
"inside NethServer 7. Choose an application and click on the "
":guilabel:`Start migration` button. In this phase the migration process "
"will install the application into the NethServer 8 cluster and start the "
"first data synchronization. If the NethServer 8 cluster is composed by 2 "
"or more nodes, you will be asked to select a destination node."
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:48
msgid ""
"You can now click the :guilabel:`Sync data` button multiple time to keep "
"in sync the application data between NethServer 7 and NethServer 8."
msgstr ""

#: ../../migration.rst:51
msgid ""
"When you're ready for the final migration, click the :guilabel:`Finish "
"migration` button. If the migrated application requires extra parameters,"
" the system will display a dialog box before proceeding. Please note that"
" most web application will need a dedicated FQDN (virtual host) after the"
" migration. Make sure the DNS record points to the NS8 node."
msgstr ""

